{"tid":94813,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"那個時代已過去。屬於那個時代的一切都不存在了。","createTime":"2017-01-25T13:18:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-25T13:42:11.000Z","uid":79353,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1401214c6e813ceec33a66fc170e95a1fe049f3a","tid":94813,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T13:18:29.000Z","msg":"那個時代已過去。 <br />\n屬於那個時代的一切都不存在了。 <br />\n<br />\n那些消逝了的歲月，彷彿隔著一塊 <br />\n積著灰塵的玻璃，看得到，抓不著。 <br />\n他一直在懷念著過去的一切。<br />\n如果他能衝破那塊積著灰塵的玻璃，<br />\n他會走回早已消逝的歲月。"},{"pid":"5307729276f3d2ae5e7b2ee9860fa9d2c0b42e94","tid":94813,"uid":39215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T13:22:54.000Z","msg":"那是一種難堪的相對，她一直羞低著頭，給他一個接近的機會。他沒有勇氣接近，她掉轉身，走了。"},{"pid":"e4e6169e90cdf9a4720968ecb6782154de493c4d","tid":94813,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T13:26:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>那是一種難堪的相對，她一直羞低著頭，給他一個接近的機會。他沒有勇氣接近，她掉轉身，走了。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n之前買左對倒，不過只睇左短篇小說版<br />\n長篇小說版本未有時間睇<br />\n遲D會睇."},{"pid":"b17397fa71846a5b206b00d440bddbc42300922e","tid":94813,"uid":39215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T13:36:33.000Z","msg":"我買咗酒徒<br />\n絲打有冇類像經歷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好鐘意王家衛既戲"},{"pid":"9465dc3cb96558ccbc75c689a2130776b46600b2","tid":94813,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T13:39:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我買咗酒徒<br />\n絲打有冇類像經歷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好鐘意王家衛既戲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇買酒徒<br />\n唔夠錢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我冇睇過王家衛既戲呀"},{"pid":"53d9b1137de92af3912654d54645c44ab077aaed","tid":94813,"uid":39215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T13:42:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我買咗酒徒<br />\n絲打有冇類像經歷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好鐘意王家衛既戲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇買酒徒<br />\n唔夠錢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我冇睇過王家衛既戲呀</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n吓...<br />\n你句對白係黎自花樣年華架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇啦 好正"}]}